</a>
</span>
<h2>
<span> <a href="//slashdot.org/story/24/10/09/1949256/after-winning-nobel-prize-geoffrey-hinton-said-he-was-proud-ilya-sutskever-fired-sam-altman">After Winning Nobel Prize, Geoffrey Hinton Said He Was Proud Ilya Sutskever 'Fired Sam Altman'</a> <span><a href="https://techcrunch.com/2024/10/09/after-winning-nobel-for-foundational-ai-work-geoffrey-hinton-says-hes-proud-ilya-sutskever-fired-sam-altman/" title="External link - https://techcrunch.com/2024/10/09/after-winning-nobel-for-foundational-ai-work-geoffrey-hinton-says-hes-proud-ilya-sutskever-fired-sam-altman/" target="_blank"> (techcrunch.com) </a></span></span>
<span><a href="//slashdot.org/story/24/10/09/1949256/after-winning-nobel-prize-geoffrey-hinton-said-he-was-proud-ilya-sutskever-fired-sam-altman#comments">22</a></span>
</h2>
